  "texts": [
    "In the second, we highlight novel opportunities for pedagogy enabled by generative AI for students to apply their knowledge.",
    "AI can provide students with role-playing scenarios in which they can practice their skills and post-simulation advice on their performance.",
    "In the third section we highlight the capacity of the AI to act as a tutor and mentor, helping students connect concepts and gain a deeper understanding of class topics.",
    "For each exercise, students are required to engage extensively with the AI and reflect on the process.",
    "In the final section we focus on AI blueprint tools that can create tools for instructors to use."
